'''''Tremors''''' is the debut studio album by English musician [[Sohn (musician)|Sohn]], released on 7 April 2014 by [[4AD]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.4ad.com/releases/664 |title=SOHN: 'Tremors' |publisher=[[4AD]] |accessdate=12 February 2017}}</ref> In 2014 it was awarded a silver certification from the [[Independent Music Companies Association]],<ref>http://www.impalamusic.org/sites/default/files/pictures/Awards5.png</ref> which indicated sales of at least 20,000 copies throughout Europe. <ref>http://www.impalamusic.org/node/340</ref>

