Credits adapted from the liner notes of ''Tremors''.<ref>{{cite AV media notes |title=Tremors |type=CD liner notes |others=[[Sohn (musician)|Sohn]] |publisher=[[4AD]] |year=2014 |id=CAD 3403CD}}</ref>

